  m_text: "Welcome to the bonus challenge!\n\nYour mission is to survive as long
    as possible while keeping the crowd away from the armoured water-cannon vehicle.\n\nEvery
    protester you \u201Ccool down\u201D earns you 10 score points.\n\nThe longer
    you last, the higher your final score.\n\nBe careful \u2014 if too many protesters
    get close to the vehicle, the level ends. You can track the vehicle\u2019s HP
    on the health bar at the bottom-center of the screen."
  m_isRightToLeft: 0
  m_fontAsset: {fileID: 11400000, guid: 8f586378b4e144a9851e7b34d9b748ee, type: 2}
